metadata.name: Boomboxhead #386
metadata.description: Boomboxheads V2 is a collection of 420 CC0 avatars on the Ethereum Network. They are 3d multi-format NFTs including artwork, a VRM avatar, and a posed GLB. The assets are available for public use under the CC0 license. This project was produced with boom-tools, an open-source project, running on Unity3d.
